OL,3,CDeli trashed by vandals after being
OL,4,Cbroken into for 20th time
OL,6,FThe owner of a popular deli and cafe
OL,7,Fsays he is at the end of his tether
OL,8,Fafter vandals forced their way into
OL,9,Fthe outdoor area and "trashed" it, for
OL,10,Fthe 20th time.
OL,12,FStaff at North Star Delicatessen on
OL,13,FWilbraham Road in Chorlton, South
OL,14,FManchester, arrived at the premises on
OL,15,FWednesday morning, 16 October, to find
OL,16,Fentry had been forced to their secure,
OL,17,Fenclosed outdoor area.
