OL,3,CDeli trashed by vandals after being
OL,4,Cbroken into for 20th time
OL,6,FManagers say CCTV footage shows a man
OL,7,Fand a woman entering the property,
OL,8,Fwhich was then ransacked. Speakers,
OL,9,Flight fittings, furniture, and
OL,10,Fcushions were all tampered with or
OL,11,Fdamaged.
OL,13,FThe pair did not enter the main
OL,14,Fbuilding and nothing was stolen.
OL,15,FHowever, owners say the vandals caused
OL,16,Fan estimated #400 worth of damage.
OL,18,FWorkers were forced to spend several
OL,19,Fhours cleaning, rearranging, and
OL,20,Fmaking the area presentable and
OL,21,Fuseable again.
