OL,3,CDeli trashed by vandals after being
OL,4,Cbroken into for 20th time
OL,6,FKonstandinos Nearchou, 38, from
OL,7,FWarrington, who opened the Greek
OL,8,Fbrunch spot in 2018, says people have
OL,9,Fbroken into, or caused damage in,
OL,10,Ftheir outdoor area on 20 occasions, at
OL,11,Fleast five of which have been reported
OL,12,Fto police.
OL,14,FProblems, he claims, include people
OL,15,Fsleeping, drinking, doing drugs and
OL,16,Fgoing to the toilet in there.
OL,18,FHe says he has invested in spotlights,
OL,19,FCCTV cameras, and fencing but that the
OL,20,Fincidents continue to occur.
