OL,3,CDeli trashed by vandals after being
OL,4,Cbroken into for 20th time
OL,6,FMr Nearchou: "It's been trashed. And
OL,7,Fthere could be no reason. It's just
OL,8,Fvandalism. Last week someone had just
OL,9,Fripped down the blinds completely. We
OL,10,Fdidn't find any drug-related items
OL,11,Fthis time.
OL,13,F"But it's often that we come in and
OL,14,Ffind people have been here sleeping,
OL,15,Fdrinking, doing drugs."
