OL,3,CDeli trashed by vandals after being
OL,4,Cbroken into for 20th time
OL,6,FMr Nearchou said after the last
OL,7,Fincident officers attended but "left
OL,8,Fafter 45 seconds" and that he was told
OL,9,Fthe "case had been closed" before he
OL,10,Fhad chance to inform them about the
OL,11,FCCTV images. He has now been told the
OL,12,Finvestigation has been "re-opened."
OL,14,FHe said he has "no idea" why his
OL,15,Frestaurant is being repeatedly hit.
