OL,3,CDeli trashed by vandals after being
OL,4,Cbroken into for 20th time
OL,6,FMr Nearchou continued: "Other places
OL,7,Fnearby also have outdoor areas. But
OL,8,Fthey don't have as many incidents, if
OL,9,Fany. I don't know why. People have
OL,10,Fsaid I must be being targeted, but I
OL,11,Fdon't want to think like this."
OL,13,F"We have done a lot, we've put CCTV
OL,14,Fin, floodlights, more security. But
OL,15,Fwe're trying to make it nice for
OL,16,Fpeople. No one wants to sit in an
OL,17,Foutdoor area that looks like a prison.
OL,18,FSo there's only so much we can do."
OL,20,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP) has
OL,21,Fbeen approached for comment.
